      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start, really sets the mood. can you expand on that? i want to get a better sense of the crowd. can you describe some of the specific groups of people that hang out in these areas? like, what do they look like, what are they wearing, and what kind of 'vibe' do they give off that makes the area feel so high-tension?",
